Package: rmdpo
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Translate R Markdown and Quarto documents using poEdit
Description: Extract each block of an R Markdown or Quarto document into a
  translatable string in .po format (editable in poEdit, or transferred into
  other translation tools). Once the strings are translated, build the
  translated version of the initial document in the same R Markdown or Quarto
  format.
